steps.html_instructions:
Head northwest on Steve Flanders Square toward Broadway/Canyon of Heroes
Restricted usage road
Steve Flanders Square turns slightly left and becomes Murray Street
Turn right onto Church St
Slight left onto 6th Ave/Avenue of the Americas
Turn left onto Watts St

Continue onto I-78 W/Clifford Milburn Holland Tunnel/Holland Tunnel
Continue to follow I-78 W
Entering New Jersey
Keep left at the fork to continue on NJ-139 W
Continue onto U.S. 1 S/U.S. 9 S
Take the exit toward US 1-9 S/New Jersey 21/US 22/Interstate 78
Continue onto US-1 Truck S/US-9 Truck S
Take the Interstate 78 W/Garden State Parkway exit
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for Interstate 78 Express W/Garden State Parkway and merge onto I-78 Express W
Continue onto I-78 Express W

Merge onto I-78 W
Partial toll road
Entering Pennsylvania
Take the Interstate 81 exit on the left toward Harrisburg
Merge onto I-81 S

Keep right at the fork to stay on I-81 S
Passing through Maryland, West Virginia, Virginia
Entering Tennessee
Take exit 1B to merge onto I-40 W toward Knoxville
Keep left at the fork to continue on I-75, follow signs for Chattanooga
Take exit 2 for I-24 W toward Chattanooga/Birmingham
Continue onto I-24 W

Keep left at the fork to stay on I-24 W, follow signs for Interstate 24 W/Interstate 59/Nashville/Birmingham
Entering Georgia
Take exit 167 on the left for I-59 S toward Birmingham

Continue onto I-59 S
Entering Alabama
Take exit 137 on the left for I-459 S toward Tuscaloosa/Montgomery
Continue onto I-459 S
Take exit 15 for Interstate 65 toward Birmingham/Montgomery
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for Interstate 65 S/Montgomery and merge onto I-65 S
Take exit 171 for Interstate 85 N/Day Street toward Atlanta
Keep left, follow signs for Interstate 85 N/Atlanta
Continue onto I-85 N
Take exit 1 for Court St
Continue onto Arba St (signs for Alabama State Univ)
Turn right onto S Decatur St

Sharp left onto S Union St
Destination will be on the right
